<title>USA: Houston Industries to buy back $300 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>Houston Industries to buy back $300 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Houston Industries Inc said on Wednesday that it expanded its previous authorization to repurchase common stock by $300 million, making the total value of the buyback plan $450 million.</p>
<p>The company said so far that it repurchased about 4.6 million shares at a total cost of $104 million between the dates June 5 and September 3.</p>
